= Howto edit this wiki with Vim =
Get source: [[topic/github]]

Then {{{ cd vim-online-wiki-source }}} so that:
* file completion {{{ctrl-x ctrl-f}}} completes internal files
* gf can be used to follow such links

You may want to install vim-addon-goto-thing-at-cursor, it behaves like gf, but
is able to create new files which don't exist.

This wiki also ships with minimal filetype and syntax support
